### Example 30: Data Cleaning and Transformation
```typescript
const csv = `id,email,status,signup_date
1,JOHN@EXAMPLE.COM,active,2024-01-01
2,jane.smith@test.com,inactive,
3,,active,2024-01-03
4,bob@company.com,active,2024-01-04`;

